values: what up??? i couldnt reply to leahs website on here for some reason, so ill do it here. you had some good pics baby i just wish i was in them. i miss you a ton and i cant wait to get home. not a damn thing happening in iraq for me and im gettin bored and just want to hold my wife. i love you

today is stressfull. i have to train these army idiots how to do their own jobs. they want to change everything we are doing and they have barely even seen a mortar attack yet. i hate when people who dont know what they are talking about suddenly think the are an expert because they are older or in this case outrank you. i have only 21 days left here though and i am so ready to be waking up next oto leah every morning like things were. we really have a great marriage and need time to enjoy it together. maybe i will actually be home for x-mas thids year too. 2005 will be better by far than last year.

this is kinda wierd, i cant type at all but my wifey does this stuff so well see what gives. i am also stuck in iraq so i cant exactly tell all that i do each day, but well see how it goes. i lokk like i will be leaving here in about a month or so so thats awesome cuz i can go back to my girl and finnjally get to be good and married. we havent spent a lot of time together so i am really looking forward to that. anyway, gonna go feed myself
